    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Once the meatballs are browned, reduce the heat to medium-high, add the<strong> sliced carrot</strong> to the pan and cook, covered, for 6 min or until starting to soften and the meatballs are cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Once soft, add your <strong>sugar snap peas</strong> and cook, uncovered, for 1 min further</p>",
