    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>rice noodles</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until softened, stirring frequently with a fork to separate the noodles</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>rice noodles</strong>, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy noodle water</strong></p>",
