    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> Vietnamese-style dressing</strong> to the pan along with the <strong>drained noodles</strong> and a splash of the<strong> reserved starchy noodle water</strong></p><p>Mix well until everything is nicely coated in the dressing – these are your <strong>Vietnamese-style chilli beef meatball noodles</strong></p>",
